ldren during the first week after vaccination, Yih said. The study is published online in the New England Journal of Medicine.\r\n\r\nIf you or a loved one may have suffered an adverse reaction to the Rotavirus or other vaccination, please <a href=\"http://myvaccinelawyer.com/contactus.html\">contact My Vaccine Lawyer</a> at (800) 229-7704 for a free consultation today.','Rotavirus Can Cause a Stomach Blockage in Infants','','inherit','closed','open','','126-revision-v1','','','2014-01-16 20:40:01','2014-01-16 20:40:01','',126,'http://myvaccinelawyer.com/blog/126-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
